## Limitations

The information gathered is based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of public health's importance. The data is limited to the perspectives provided by the selected sources, and there may be other viewpoints or recent developments not covered in this report. Additionally, the search was conducted in English, potentially excluding non-English sources that could offer further insights.